Package: AntBoost
Title: Demonstrating the Isomorphism Between Boosting and Ant Colony Recruitment
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Ernest", "Fokoué", email = "epfeqa@rit.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Gregory", "Babbitt", email = "gabsbi@rit.edu", role = "aut"),
    person("Yuval", "Levental", email = "yhl3051@rit.edu", role = "aut")
    )
Description: Implements both AdaBoost and Ant Colony Adaptive Recruitment (ACAR),
    demonstrating their mathematical isomorphism as established in "Isomorphic 
    Functionalities between Ant Colony and Ensemble Learning: Part II". Provides
    simulation tools, visualization functions, and an interactive Shiny app for
    exploring the boosting–ant colony correspondence.
